\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 No? And what about your mother, I think it would be helpful if you said a little bit more, I think, about your relationship with her. }{
