\par Stuart:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 Well, the lower middle-class and Trade Union workers. They are the Independence [leaders]. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
