\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 Could you talk about some of those people from the British Left, then? You\rquote 
ve mentioned Chuck and Raphael, but could you say something about them \endash  what sort of people they were? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid7739222\charrsid7739222 
\par 
\par Stuart:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 Well, you know, Raphael was an extraordinary person, of course! (LAUGHS) And you know Raphael\rquote s background \endash 
 in the Communist Party, around that circle. Other people there \endash  Peter Sedgwick, Raphael, Pet
er, Gabriel Pearson, Stanley Mitchell, so a small group. Okay? They were mainly in Balliol, mainly under the wing of Christopher Hill, though not all of them. All of them very clever, and they were, of course, banned from taking part in Labour Party meeti
n
gs, but they could go to the Labour Club. There was both the meetings of the Labour Party - students would belong to the Labour Party on Sunday mornings, and there were meetings of the Labour Club, like the Socialist Club, or the Communist Party, they had
 
public meetings at other times, so they were intermediary between the two. They were kind of keepers of the conscience of the Left. But remember, this is the deep Cold War, so huge suspicion of Communists, and of anybody that far, and a lot of people, wel
l
, they loved Raphael, he was a kind of figure in Oxford, of course, you can imagine, so nobody ever boycotted Raphael, but they were a bit suspicious about what the Communists were up to. Everybody was a bit suspicious about what the Communists were up to
, and it wasn\rquote t until \rquote 56, around \rquote 56, or in the fall before that, that there was a mingling of the different factions and tendencies on the Left, into a wider formation. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid7739222\charrsid7739222 
