Yes. The cultural was a clear line, an independent line of interest, which distinguished us from a more economistic Marxism, or a more - I nearly said \'93Weberian\'94, but I don\rquote 
t mean that - a more social class kind of social democratic politics. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid7739222\charrsid7739222 
