m not sure of the dates of the Partisan. Would it have been the same kind of time as you launched ULR? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid7739222\charrsid7739222 
