\par Stuart:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 
Yes! And we had six children for tea, we would have them, and then ours would go to the Coyles [Robert and Anglea], and then the Coyles would go to other people, etc., a big network in which neighbourhood Feminism, Feminis
t politics, and academic interest overlapped. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid7739222\charrsid7739222 
