\par Stuart:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 Oh yes. Yes. Yes. But I didn\rquote t really get to know him at school. He was a big boy, and he was just leaving \endash 
 he was in the sixth form \endash  and I was younger than him. But I met him later than that. I\rquote ve interviewed him several times. In fact, there\rquote s an interview with him on the
 playing fields of Jamaica College (LAUGHS) in the film that I made for the BBC \endash 
 the series that I made, called Redemption Song. I made seven programmes in the late eighties/early nineties, about the different cultures that went into the making of the Car
ibbean, and I interviewed him at Jamaica College. So we became friends like that. But my closer friends were, you know, active in the leadership of the PNP, or they were teachers at the University, West Indian historians, or they were students making trou
ble in the seventies. What I felt about that was, \'93I know these people very much, but I haven\rquote t lived that life. That\rquote s not the life I\rquote ve lived\'94. That\rquote s what my family blocked. If I\rquote 
d have gone back home, I would have been exactly part of that. But I wasn\rquote t. So I had to find a way of re-connecting with it \endash  through my work, through my reading, through my thinking, \'93
What was that experience about? Why was it so alienating? What is the way of accommodating with it so that it doesn\rquote t undermine you emotionally or intellectually?\'94 I came to see it as a problem because I couldn\rquote 
t reconstitute it as a kind of continuous part of my life. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid7739222\charrsid7739222 
\par 
\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 But the thing is that that \endash  what was going on in Jamaica \endash 
 was something you were very conscious of, and it was part of your self, even if you couldn\rquote t have an active part in it? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid7739222\charrsid7739222 
