t go on doing that, and in any case I didn\rquote t want to be beholden to him, so I decided to leave Oxford, with it unfinished, and get a job in London. So I moved to London, and that\rquote s 19 - well, I took my degree in 1957. Okay? }{\rtlch\fcs1 
