\par Stuart:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 
And well, what was I to do? (LAUGHS) Oxford, no. M.A., hoping to be a D.Phil., but meanwhile not a social skill in the world! (LAUGHS) Could I drive a milk float? No, I didn\rquote t have a lice
nce then! Well, I could be a secondary school teacher. I could be a supply teacher. So I got a job. I went to live in Clapham. I was given an introduction to a family there \endash  the Hastons \endash  have I spoken about them? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
