\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 Oh, tell me about that, then, please. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
