\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 I think it was called the Chelsea College of Science. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
