\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 That\rquote s interesting. Now, when we broke off, you\rquote 
d been talking about your theoretical ideas, and I think we covered most of that, but there\rquote s one bit which you \endash  I\rquote m sure we would have come to it if we\rquote d gone on \endash 
 which was the influence of interactionism and Howard Becker. Could you say something about that? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid7739222\charrsid7739222 
