ve got quite a clear idea now of how it all worked, and the ideas. Would it be possible to talk about some of the people who were there? I\rquote m thinking, for instance, there was this core group, in a way, that wrote - well, there are two books 
\endash  Resistance to Rituals, and Policing the Crisis. Some of those people could you say something about? Who were they? Where did they come from? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
