ry open period, and later we move into a much more structured university era when it would be very difficult to imagine what you were doing. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid7739222\charrsid7739222 

