, if you gather people, a group of interested people together, and start to read and converse in detail, they soon start to think, \'93Well, let\rquote s work together on this or that\'94. In the wake of the 1968 occupations \endash  student occupations 
\endash  we did a long study of the treatment of the press of such events. People who had been involved, then constructed the occupation as an analytic event. We tried to study, research and analyse. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
