\par Stuart:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 Well, if I have, okay. I mean, I said the Grundrisse, yes? Marx was a continuous point of reference. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
