\par Stuart:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 I did, in the end. Yes. So I taught Summer Schools, and I did a bit of teaching of my own. But it\rquote 
s not the same. The staff, the academic staff is differently related to the student experience in the OU, than it is in other places. It\rquote 
s not, in that sense, a teaching role, except through word and through the courses, through supervising the exams, and looking at essays, etc., but it\rquote s not a lecturing role. Course units are our lectures. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
