\par Stuart:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 Oh yes, there were lots of people, but you do remember that there aren\rquote t students in the same way, yes? So you don\rquote 
t have the same relationship as a lecturer with an undergraduate audience. I used to teach courses, but that\rquote s separate, and you do that once a week or 
