\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 Okay. Well, I think that clarifies that very well. Now, on ideas, one of the things which struck me was that \endash  I think you
\rquote ve given me a very clear picture of your evolving attitude to Marxism in general, except that while you mentioned Althusser once or twice, it\rquote 
s not really quite clear how there your ideas changed, developed and changed. It would be interesting to hear about that. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid7739222\charrsid7739222 
