\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 Yes. Well, I wanted to ask you about your meaning of \'93modernity\'94. It\rquote s a word that you seem to be very keen on keeping. }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid7739222\charrsid7739222 
