\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 
Okay, well I think I understand that all right now! Thank you. Now, the next topic I thought we could spend some time on is your interest in the visual arts. I have the impression this goes back really a long way \'85 }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
