\par Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3228552\charrsid3228552 That\rquote s from the Commonwealth, isn\rquote t it? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
